metadata.name: ENCODE GOLD KEY
metadata.description:
This is one of the strictly limited ENCODE GRAPHICS FOUNDER KEYS that will give you access to various products and services on our WEB3 platform [ENCODE NETWORK](https://encode.network). So, this key is a general MINT PASS and will also allow you to read all the comics, participate in raffles and get other goodies in terms of subscription. 

ENCODE Graphics is a young book and art publisher that actually emerged from the NFT scene and focuses on futuristic themes. The myths of the crypto scene and the digital and virtual worlds have a firm place and are expressed in narrative form and various artistic representations. More information can be found on our [main website](https://www.encode.graphics/). ENCODE was founded in 2020 by PR1MAL CYPHER.

You can check which items this key claimed by going to [this link](https://encode.network/key-checker/1)
